  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a multicenter, open-label, observational, postmarketing surveillance study that
      will collect information on the use of Genentech GH preparations to treat GH-deficient
      subjects with optimal GH dosing during puberty.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
